title: The Vampire Diaries Cast Shares Photos From the Final Day on Set
text:
Nina Dobrev Says Goodbye to The Vampire Diaries With Cast Next Up The Most Anticipated New Winter Shows 
Meteroloigists have it wrong: that water filling the streets of Atlanta at the moment probably isn't from the thunderstorms walloping the region but the symbolic tears of The Vampire Diaries cast, crew and fans mourning the last day of shooting for the series. 
As Mystical Falls prepares to be a thing of the, uh, mystic past in the lead up to The CW's beloved series' finale on Friday, March 10, the people of Julie Plec 's scary-good supernatural drama naturally took to social media Wednesday to celebrate-slash-grieve (celegrieve?).
